    <div class="contact-eyebrow">Get in touch</div>
    <h2 class="contact-title">Let's talk about your energy needs.</h2>
    <p class="contact-body">Whether you're sizing a new solar setup, replacing an inverter, or looking for bulk supply — we're happy to help you find the right solution.</p>
    <div class="contact-details">
